## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="02553-102">A tabela a seguir mostra as opções com suporte no momento.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="02553-102">The following table shows the currently supported options.</span></span>  
  
|<span data-ttu-id="02553-103">Categoria</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="02553-103">Category</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="02553-104">Configuração</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="02553-104">Setting</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="02553-105">Valor/efeito</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="02553-105">Value/effect</span></span>|  
|--------------|-------------|-------------------|  
|<span data-ttu-id="02553-106">contrato</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="02553-106">contract</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="02553-107">herança</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="02553-107">inheritance</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="02553-108">`true` Para ativar a herança de contrato; `false` para desativá-lo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="02553-108">`true` to turn contract inheritance on; `false` to turn it off.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="02553-109">O padrão é `true`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="02553-109">The default is `true`.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="02553-110">tempo de execução</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="02553-110">runtime</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="02553-111">verificando</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="02553-111">checking</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="02553-112">`true` Para ativar a verificação de tempo de execução em; `false` para desativá-lo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="02553-112">`true` to turn run-time checking on; `false` to turn it off.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="02553-113">O padrão é `true`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="02553-113">The default is `true`.</span></span>|  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="02553-114">Você pode usar esse atributo, conforme ilustrado nos exemplos a seguir.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="02553-114">You can use this attribute as illustrated in the following examples.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="02553-115">Para desativar a verificação de todo o assembly de tempo de execução:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="02553-115">To turn off run-time checking for the entire assembly:</span></span>  
  
```  
[assembly:ContractOption("runtime", "checking", false)]  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="02553-116">Para ativar a verificação de contrato de tempo de execução para um tipo específico:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="02553-116">To turn run-time contract checking on for a specific type:</span></span>  
  
```  
   [ContractOption("runtime", "checking", true)]  
   class TypeWithRuntimeChecking {  
  
       ...  
  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="02553-117">Para desativar a verificação de tempo de execução para um método específico:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="02553-117">To turn run-time checking off for a specific method:</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
// Turn off all contract inheritance from interface IList<T>  
[ContractOption("contract", "inheritance", false)]  
class MyConcurrentList<T> : IList<T> {  
   ...  
}  
  
[ContractOption("runtime", "checking", false)]  
public override MyMethod(int x) {  
   // no inherited contracts checked at runtime,  
   // no invariants checked at runtime.  
   ...  
}  
  
       [ContractOption("runtime", "checking", false)]  
       public void MethodWithoutRuntimeChecking(...) {  
          ...  
       }  
   }  
  
```
